sequenceDiagram
    participant a as Alice
    participant b as Bob
    a->>b: solid filled
    b-->>a: dashed filled
    a->b: solid open
    b-->a: dashed open
    a->>a: note to self
    Note left of a: on the left
    Note right of b: on the right
    Note over a: over one
    Note over a,b: spanning both
